{"id": "1195807097095463052", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Dont forget to pull for this. \nIt is Sorel's equipment (Wheel of Life, that is the name of equipments in the game)", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:10:28.969000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1195807096701194390", "filename": "Screenshot_20240113-200807.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2199703, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1170692781216378960/1195807096701194390/Screenshot_20240113-200807.png?ex=6a378e64&is=6a363ce4&hm=8c4fb533c227604d2ca17df4a83e7c79ae4a07d48f0bde7504eca6fbbfc5d709&"}]}
{"id": "1195808384327352410", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "As for understanding the skill, you need to know what the skill does in the first place before understanding what you should do and how to play a stage. \nSo the basic way of doing that is learning the basic yellow squad given to you at the start.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:15:35.869000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195808426245234698", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Ramona is debuffer/buffer and damage dealer.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:15:45.863000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195808437725040690", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Rotan is purely damage dealer and when you later equip the scissors wheel of life on her she becomes a debuffer.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:15:48.600000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195808510848552961", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Dole is the healer/debuffer of the team.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:16:06.034000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195808513956511846", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Ogier the knight is the shielded for the team.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:16:06.775000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195808702482087977", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Prioritize shields than heals for the team because shield can outlast your HP. \nMost times, you want the shield to outlast incoming damage in a round at best and worst, reduce the damage you take that depletes your HP.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:16:51.723000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195809016866152519", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Rotan 3 cost card works in a way were the cost of the card reduces by -1 for every \"strike/blow\" card played. In other games, we know this as basic attack.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T19:18:06.678000+00:00"}
