{"id": "1195826079168991292", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "699865304146116628", "author_name": "tsukineesan", "content": "And what does Embryo fusion means", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:25:54.648000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195826824840749179", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Have you used Red?\nIf you have, there are little Embryo that can be merged with the Ultimate of Red characters for additional attributes.\nBut they can also be used to grant 30 Energy for Ultimate if directly used.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:28:52.430000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195827047063363714", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Rose uses infinite amount, she's the first. The other Red use 1 embryo for their special effect during ultimate.\nEvery Red has that.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:29:45.412000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195827117485727834", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "699865304146116628", "author_name": "tsukineesan", "content": "ouh", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:30:02.202000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195827160137613362", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "699865304146116628", "author_name": "tsukineesan", "content": "I think I understand, kinda", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:30:12.371000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195827388760719510", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "699865304146116628", "author_name": "tsukineesan", "content": "Okay but what does her skill do?", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:31:06.879000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195827645439549611", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "699865304146116628", "author_name": "tsukineesan", "content": "ATK and Defense are the same as StS but idk what Awaken, Jeweled Egg and Beauty of Roses is", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:32:08.076000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195829334448017468", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Every Character has their Awaken card, this usually gives additional gameplay mechanics to the characters. \nRose Awaken allows her to gain more strength for every attack she does. \n\nJewelled Egg is a skill that allows you gain HP at the end of a round. This depends on how much attack is dealt by the team. This skill should be used 1st in  a round when you want to deal damage in that round. \n\nBeauty of Roses is her attack skill that deals damage to enemies, will deal more when you meet a condition and heal. The condition is a certain HP threshold. \n\nHer \"ATK\" or \"Strike\" card as it is know, deals more damage at a certain HP threshold as well. \n\nYou'll know when it does more damage as the card will have a Yellow Aura on it.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:38:50.767000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195830694241382410", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:44:14.967000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1195830693201191022", "filename": "Recording_2024-01-13-21-40-52.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 29860852, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1170692781216378960/1195830693201191022/Recording_2024-01-13-21-40-52.mp4?ex=6a37a45e&is=6a3652de&hm=c75ea4419ca765b8c4833b8c9e3467008e5feb44558b580cd2f5683854efaf5e&"}]}
{"id": "1195831105266393209", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "Dunoo if this helps in anyway, but I'll just drop it. \nNotice how I played Jewelled Egg first before attacking? That's because you gain more HP when you attack after playing Jewelled Egg card.", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:45:52.963000+00:00"}
{"id": "1195831702631764170", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "content": "The red fetus like cards are known as embryos. \nUse them directly to gain 30 ultimate energy or use ultimate and you'll \"devour\".", "timestamp": "2024-01-13T20:48:15.386000+00:00"}
